title: SOL CAL Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, American, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe and market using organic, gmo-free, unrefined ingredients. Offers cold pressed juice, smoothies, veggie burgers, salads, pasta, bowls, tacos, acai bowls, and seasonal specials. Est. 2014 as vegetarian, then remodeled and made menu changes in Jan 2016.
